<ul style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">
	<li>সকল প্রতীক/অক্ষর 90&deg; ঘড়ির কাঁটার বিপরীত দিকে ঘুরছে।</li>
</ul>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/12/F1_Sourav_SSC_6_12_24_471.png" style="width: 339px; height: 81px;" /></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">সুতরাং, সঠিক উত্তর হল <span style="font-weight: bolder;">"বিকল্প </span><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-weight: 700;">3</span><span style="font-weight: bolder;">"</span></p>

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Family Chart:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage13914.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Given:&amp;nbsp;A is the husband of B. B is the sister of C. C is the brother of D. D is the father of E. E is the wife of F.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6724ad01b814081b01c2f6af.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, D is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Wife&amp;#39;s father&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;of F.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Wife&amp;#39;s father&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">পরিবারের চার্ট:</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><img alt="" src="https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage13914.png" /></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">প্রদত্ত: A, B-র স্বামী। B, C-র বোন। C, D-র ভাই। D, E-র বাবা। E, F-র স্ত্রী।</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><img alt="" src="//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6724ad01b814081b01c2f6af.png" /></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">সুতরাং, D, F-র '<strong><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">স্ত্রীর বাবা</span></strong>'।</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">অতএব, সঠিক উত্তর হল <span style="font-weight: bolder;">"স্ত্রীর বাবা"</span><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">।&nbsp;</span></p>

