&lt;p data-darkreader-inline-color=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); --darkreader-inline-color: #d1cdc7;&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;vuuw&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>এখানে অনুসৃত যুক্তি হল:</p>

