questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;By interchanging which two signs and two numbers (not digits) the equation will be correct?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;5 + 9 - 3 &amp;times; 8 &amp;divide; 2 = 10&lt;/p&gt;<br><p>কোন দুটি চিহ্ন এবং দুটি সংখ্যা (অঙ্ক নয়) পরস্পর বিনিময় করলে সমীকরণটি সঠিক হবে?</p>

<p>5 + 9 - 3 x 8 &divide; 2 = 10</p>

questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage671384fa1fccbfbfbab4aa64.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Given equation:&amp;nbsp;5 + 9 - 3 &amp;times; 8 &amp;divide; 2 = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times;&amp;nbsp;and +, 9 and 3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;By interchanging&amp;nbsp;two signs and two numbers (not digits):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;5 &lt;/span&gt;&amp;times;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt; 3 - 9 + &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8 &amp;divide; 2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = 10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5 &amp;times; 3&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; - 9 + 4 = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;15&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; - 9 &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;+ 4&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;19 - 9&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;strong&gt;10 = 10&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 2)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;divide; and &amp;times;, 9 and 3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;By interchanging&amp;nbsp;two signs and two numbers (not digits):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;5 + 3 - &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9 &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;divide;&lt;/span&gt; 8 &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times;&lt;/span&gt; 2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;5 + 3 - 2.25&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 5.75 = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 3)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;+ and -, 5 and 3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;By interchanging&amp;nbsp;two signs and two numbers (not digits):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;3 - 9 + &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5 &amp;times; 8 &amp;divide; 2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/u&gt; - 9 +&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;23 - 9&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 14 = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 4)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and &amp;divide;, 5 and 3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;By interchanging&amp;nbsp;two signs and two numbers (not digits):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;3 + 9 - &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5 &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;divide;&lt;/span&gt; 8 &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times;&lt;/span&gt; 2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3 + 9 - 1.25&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 10.75&amp;nbsp;= 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;times;&amp;nbsp;and +, 9 and 3&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><img src="https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage671384fa1fccbfbfbab4aa64.png" /></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">প্রদত্ত সমীকরণ: 5 + 9 - 3 x 8 &divide; 2 = 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><strong>বিকল্প 1) <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">x এবং +, 9 এবং 3</span></strong></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">দুটি চিহ্ন এবং দুটি সংখ্যা (অঙ্ক নয়) পরস্পর বিনিময় করে:</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr;&nbsp;5&nbsp;&times;&nbsp;3 - 9 +&nbsp;<u><span style="font-weight: bolder;">8 &divide; 2</span></u>&nbsp;= 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr;&nbsp;<u><span style="font-weight: bolder;">5 &times; 3</span></u>&nbsp;- 9 + 4 = 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr;&nbsp;<u><span style="font-weight: bolder;">15</span></u>&nbsp;- 9&nbsp;<u><span style="font-weight: bolder;">+ 4</span></u>&nbsp;= 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr;&nbsp;<u><span style="font-weight: bolder;">19 - 9</span></u>&nbsp;= 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr;&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bolder;">10 = 10</span></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">বিকল্প 2) <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&divide; এবং x, 9 এবং 3</span></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">দুটি চিহ্ন এবং দুটি সংখ্যা (অঙ্ক নয়) পরস্পর বিনিময় করে:</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr; 5 + 3 - <u><strong>9 <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&divide;</span> 8 <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">x</span> 2</strong></u> = 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr; <strong><u>5 + 3 - 2.25</u></strong> = 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr; 5.75 = 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">বিকল্প 3) <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">+ এবং -, 5 এবং 3</span></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">দুটি চিহ্ন এবং দুটি সংখ্যা (অঙ্ক নয়) পরস্পর বিনিময় করে:</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr; 3 - 9 + <u><strong>5 x 8 &divide; 2</strong></u> = 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr; <u><em><strong>3</strong></em></u> - 9 + </span><u style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">20</span></u><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"> = 10</span></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr; <u><strong>23 - 9</strong></u> = 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr; 14 = 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">বিকল্প 4) <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">x</span><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"> এবং &divide;, 5 এবং 3</span></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">দুটি চিহ্ন এবং দুটি সংখ্যা (অঙ্ক নয়) পরস্পর বিনিময় করে:</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr; 3 + 9 - <u><strong>5 <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&divide;</span> 8 <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">x</span> 2</strong></u> = 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr; <u><strong>3 + 9 - 1.25</strong></u> = 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&rArr; 10.75 = 10</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">সুতরাং, সঠিক উত্তর হল "</span><span style="font-weight: bolder;">x এবং +, 9 এবং 3"</span></p>

