questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The&amp;nbsp;best completes the pattern given:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/12/F1_Sourav_SSC_6_12_24_356.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 1&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">নিচের চিত্রটি প্রদত্ত প্যাটার্ন সবচেয়ে ভালোভাবে সম্পূর্ণ করে:</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/12/F1_Sourav_SSC_6_12_24_356.png" /></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">অতএব, সঠিক উত্তর হল <span style="font-weight: bolder;">"বিকল্প 1".</span></p>

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;@ means -, # means -, * means&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;divide;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;10 @ 5 # 15 * 5 = 2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;10 - 5 - 15&amp;nbsp;&amp;divide; 5 = 10 - 5 - 3 = 2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;25 @ 6 # 4 * 2 = 17&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;25 - 6 - 4&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;divide; 2 = 25 - 6 - 2 = 17&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Similarly, 30 @ 10 # 20 * 4 = ?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;30 - 10 - 20&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;divide; 4 = 30 - 10 - 5 = &lt;strong&gt;15&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;15&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">এখানে ব্যবহৃত যুক্তি হল:</span></p>

<p><strong>@ মানে -, # মানে -, * মানে <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&divide;</span></strong></p>

<p>10 @ 5 # 15 * 5 = 2</p>

<p>10 - 5 - 15 &divide; 5 = 10 - 5 - 3 = 2</p>

<p>25 @ 6 # 4 * 2 = 17</p>

<p>25 - 6 - 4 <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&divide; 2 = 25 - 6 - 2 = 17</span></p>

<p>একইভাবে, 30 @ 10 # 20 * 4 = ?</p>

<p>30 - 10 - 20 <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&divide; 4 = 30 - 10 - 5 = <strong>15</strong></span></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">অতএব, সঠিক উত্তর হল </span><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-weight: 700;">"15".</span></p>

