questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6710c3a69a350a9081c5a2ce.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;GT ∶ HV&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;G + 1 = H; T + 2 = V&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Similarly,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;DQ&amp;nbsp;∶&amp;nbsp;ES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;D + 1 = E; Q + 2 = S;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;DQ&amp;nbsp;∶&amp;nbsp;ES&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><img src="https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6710c3a69a350a9081c5a2ce.png" /></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">এখানে ব্যবহৃত লজিক হল:</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">GT ∶ HV</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">G + 1 = H; T + 2 = V</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">একইভাবে, <strong><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">DQ ∶ ES</span></strong></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><strong>D + 1 = E; Q + 2 = S;</strong></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">অতএব, সঠিক উত্তর হল <strong>"DQ ∶ ES"।</strong></span></p>

